parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The illumination of the airbag warning light can indicate a potential problem with the airbag system, which can lead to failure to deploy or improper deployment in the event of an accident, resulting in serious injury or death.
symptoms: The airbag warning light stays on
the airbag warning light is illuminated intermittently
the airbag system is not functioning properly
the airbag did not deploy in an accident.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag to deploy in an accident can result in serious injury or death.
symptoms: The airbag did not deploy in an accident
the airbag failed to deploy despite meeting the deployment criteria.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: A malfunctioning airbag system can lead to failure to deploy or improper deployment in the event of an accident, resulting in serious injury or death.
symptoms: The airbag system is not functioning properly
the airbag warning light is illuminated
the airbag did not deploy in an accident
